uency-Inverse Document Frequency)\n- **Count Vectorization**\n- **Cosine Similarity**\n- **IMDB Bayesian Weighted Rating**\n- **Text Preprocessing & NLP**\n- **Data Cleaning & Feature Engineering**","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"---\n##  Section 1 — Import Libraries","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"# ── Core Libraries ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nimport pandas as pd\nimport numpy as np\nimport re\nimport warnings\nwarnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n\n# ── Visualization ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nimport matplotlib.pyplot as plt\nimport matplotlib.patches as mpatches\nimport seaborn as sns\n\n# ── NLP & ML ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nfrom sklearn.feature_extraction.text import TfidfVectorizer, CountVectorizer\nfrom sklearn.metrics.pairwise import cosine_similarity\nfrom sklearn.preprocessing import MinMaxScaler\n\n# ── Settings ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\npd.set_option('display.max_columns', None)\npd.set_option('display.max_colwidth', 80)\npd.set_option('display.float_format', '{:.2f}'.format)\nsns.set_theme(style='darkgrid', palette='muted')\nplt.rcParams['figure.figsize'] = (12, 5)\nplt.rcParams['figure.dpi'] = 120\n\nprint(' All libraries imported successfully!')\nprint(f'   pandas     : {pd.__version__}')\nprint(f'   numpy      : {np.__version__}')\nimport sklearn; print(f'   sklearn    : {sklearn.__version__}')","metadata":{"trusted":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2026-03-24T12:05:49.946074Z","iopub.execute_input":"2026-03-24T12:05:49.946358Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-03-24T12:05:49.953952Z","shell.execute_reply.started":"2026-03-24T12:05:49.946333Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-03-24T12:05:49.953205Z"}},"outputs":[],"execution_count":null},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"---\n## Section 2 — Load & Inspect Dataset","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"df = pd.read_cs